#O  Cone( <G> )
##  
##  <#GAPDoc Label="Cone">
##  <ManSection>
##  <Oper Name="Cone" Arg="G"/>
##  <Description>
##  
##  <P/>Returns the cone of graph <A>G</A>. The cone of <A>G</A> is
##  the graph obtained from <A>G</A> by adding a new vertex which is
